<div class="language- line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="shiki" data-ext="" data-title="" style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#abb2bf;--shiki-light-bg:#FAFAFA;--shiki-dark-bg:#282c34"><pre v-pre class="shiki shiki-themes one-light one-dark-pro vp-code"><code><span class="line"><span>一、线程安全</span></span>
<span class="line"><span>   String 天然不可变 → 多线程随意共享，无需加锁</span></span>
<span class="line"><span>   这是 Java 并发编程中最省心的类型</span></span>
<span class="line"><span></span></span>
<span class="line"><span>二、字符串常量池</span></span>
<span class="line"><span>   只有不可变，同一个字符串字面量才能被多处安全共享</span></span>
<span class="line"><span>   如果 String 可变，常量池就毫无意义</span></span>
<span class="line"><span></span></span>
<span class="line"><span>三、Hash 缓存</span></span>
<span class="line"><span>   String 经常作为 HashMap 的 key</span></span>
<span class="line"><span>   不可变意味着 hashCode 可以放心缓存，永远不变</span></span>
